Be it business or leisure, small informal dinner or dine out with friends, Raviz Calicut offers you with the best dining options in a contemporary setting. Be it the Mavoor Cafe, Keraleeyam or Pergola, Raviz Calicut present a new experience while retaining the flavours and fragrances of the original cuisines.
